I'll treat you to the ticket.

995
01:32:06,564 --> 01:32:08,156
You will?

996
01:32:09,767 --> 01:32:12,463
If you can get a seat belt
around that.

997
01:32:13,538 --> 01:32:17,133
I never use seat belts.
I don't believe in gravity.

998
01:32:19,544 --> 01:32:23,002
We both lost our men
through a shooting.

999
01:32:23,080 --> 01:32:25,173
I don't mind that Dave's dead.

1000
01:32:25,249 --> 01:32:28,844
It just means he'll be
reincarnated sooner, that's all.

1001
01:32:30,421 --> 01:32:33,254
You mean Cookie's coming back?

1002
01:32:33,324 --> 01:32:36,259
Sure! Everything comes back.

1003
01:32:39,230 --> 01:32:41,790
You know,
you look after people good.

1004
01:32:44,669 --> 01:32:47,797
I never had to look after anybody.

1005
01:32:49,307 --> 01:32:52,333
I was a princess!

1006
01:33:07,492 --> 01:33:10,359
I like that...
making the news.

1007
01:33:19,270 --> 01:33:21,795
Who was Bugsy Siegel?

1008
01:33:24,642 --> 01:33:26,803
The meanest, the coldest.

1009
01:33:26,878 --> 01:33:30,405
- And he was your cellmate?
- I gotta be honest.

1010
01:33:30,481 --> 01:33:32,676
- I was in the slammer on a D&D.
- What's that?

1011
01:33:32,750 --> 01:33:34,718
D&D. Drunk and disorderly.

1012
01:33:34,785 --> 01:33:38,186
They brought Bugsy in for ten
minutes on the way to Leavenwon'th.

1013
01:33:38,256 --> 01:33:40,918
Man, was he pissed off.

1014
01:33:40,992 --> 01:33:42,983
He didn't even know me.

1015
01:33:44,095 --> 01:33:46,063
And that's all?

1016
01:33:49,467 --> 01:33:52,197
I never killed anybody in my life.

1017
01:33:53,671 --> 01:33:56,333
I never thought you did.

1018
01:33:56,407 --> 01:33:59,171
But I did tonight.
You saw it.

1019
01:34:00,545 --> 01:34:02,570
Yeah, I saw it.

1020
01:34:07,885 --> 01:34:09,648
Some champagne?

1021
01:34:15,927 --> 01:34:19,260
You got all those young guys.
Bernie.

1022
01:34:21,499 --> 01:34:24,263
You could still see them.

1023
01:34:24,335 --> 01:34:26,326
I'm an old man.

1024
01:34:30,341 --> 01:34:32,832
Is this a proposal?

1025
01:34:36,781 --> 01:34:39,477
Anyone ever take care of you
like I did?

1026
01:34:39,550 --> 01:34:41,484
You feel safe?

1027
01:34:41,552 --> 01:34:42,883
Yes.

1028
01:34:42,954 --> 01:34:44,979
They got nice weather in Florida.

1029
01:34:45,056 --> 01:34:47,923
They've got great food in France.

1030
01:34:47,992 --> 01:34:50,153
But I got a lot of friends
down there.

1031
01:34:50,227 --> 01:34:53,094
I'll buy you new clothes.
I'll show you off.

1032
01:34:53,164 --> 01:34:54,927
Show off what?

1033
01:34:54,999 --> 01:34:58,457
You know. Just let the boys see
how well I turned out.

1034
01:34:58,536 --> 01:34:59,969
Please.

1035
01:35:01,606 --> 01:35:03,039
Come.

1036
01:35:05,676 --> 01:35:08,474
I've never been to Florida.

1037
01:35:08,546 --> 01:35:12,107
"An update on that double murder
in Atlantic City.

1038
01:35:12,183 --> 01:35:16,415
"News watcher Connie Bishop
is standing by. Come in, Connie.

1039
