1041
01:35:23,594 --> 01:35:27,360
Hey, that's me! That's me!

1042
01:35:27,431 --> 01:35:32,926
"Anyone with information should
please call the Atlantic City hot line.

1043
01:35:33,004 --> 01:35:35,495
We'll stop on the way down
and buy all the newspapers.

1044
01:35:35,573 --> 01:35:37,768
This story's gonna be big
all over the country.

1045
01:35:37,842 --> 01:35:42,006
"Gangland slaying rips apart
Atlantic City."

1046
01:35:42,079 --> 01:35:45,242
"All calls will be kept confidential.

1047
01:35:46,317 --> 01:35:48,251
France is very nice.

1048
01:35:48,319 --> 01:35:51,482
"WNBP Channel 7, Philadelphia.

1049
01:36:45,476 --> 01:36:49,503
Grace? Grace, is that you?
Hello?

1050
01:36:49,580 --> 01:36:53,072
How dare you wake me up
in the middle of the night!

1051
01:36:53,150 --> 01:36:58,019
Where the hell are you?
I have a pregnant child here.

1052
01:36:58,089 --> 01:37:00,057
You're supposed
to make me feel safe.

1053
01:37:00,124 --> 01:37:03,890
Did you see the news? The two hoods
that got killed? Guess who did it.

1054
01:37:03,961 --> 01:37:05,895
Where the hell are you?

1055
01:37:05,963 --> 01:37:07,988
Grace, did you hear what I said?

1056
01:37:08,065 --> 01:37:11,432
The murderer they're looking for...
that was me.

1057
01:37:11,502 --> 01:37:14,596
What do you mean?
You?

1058
01:37:14,672 --> 01:37:19,632
Don't kid me. You must be kidding.
You're going soft in the head?

1059
01:37:19,710 --> 01:37:21,302
That was you?

1060
01:37:23,614 --> 01:37:27,209
- Those are dangerous men.
- I wish you could be here.

1061
01:37:27,284 --> 01:37:30,515
I wish I could too.
Will you tell me where you are?

1062
01:37:30,588 --> 01:37:32,783
No, I can't tell you where I'm at.

1063
01:37:32,857 --> 01:37:36,122
Who is with you?
Is it that girl upstairs?

1064
01:37:36,193 --> 01:37:38,093
I'm alone.
There's nobody here. Just me.

1065
01:37:38,162 --> 01:37:39,959
All alone.

1066
01:37:42,166 --> 01:37:44,760
Will you shut up and listen?

1067
01:37:58,182 --> 01:38:02,744
I can hear someone around there.
I know you're not by yourself.

1068
01:38:09,727 --> 01:38:12,195
And I have had it.

1069
01:38:12,263 --> 01:38:15,255
You get back here within
five minutes or you are fired!

1070
01:38:15,332 --> 01:38:18,563
- I'll talk to you later.
- I'm not amused any longer.

1071
01:38:27,344 --> 01:38:28,777
Good morning.

1072
01:38:33,217 --> 01:38:34,946
It's light out.

1073
01:38:35,019 --> 01:38:37,112
Yeah.

1074
01:38:37,188 --> 01:38:39,122
Jeez, I'm thirsty.

1075
01:38:39,190 --> 01:38:41,658
- You want some juice?
- No.

1076
01:38:42,793 --> 01:38:45,626
Want me to go out
and get something?

1077
