No. I'll go get it.
Why don't you rest?

1078
01:38:48,365 --> 01:38:50,629
No, I'd love to go.

1079
01:38:50,701 --> 01:38:52,362
But I'm...

1080
01:38:52,436 --> 01:38:55,428
I'd really like some pizza.
