1081
01:38:55,506 --> 01:38:57,565
I love pizza.
I'll get it.

1082
01:38:59,076 --> 01:39:00,668
We'll flip.

1083
01:39:03,013 --> 01:39:04,446
Heads.

1084
01:39:12,690 --> 01:39:14,123
You win.

1085
01:39:15,092 --> 01:39:17,026
Want any money?

1086
01:39:19,296 --> 01:39:21,662
You'll need these.

1087
01:39:23,834 --> 01:39:25,267
Thanks.

1088
01:39:31,976 --> 01:39:35,537
So, what do you like...
anchovies, mushrooms?

1089
01:39:35,613 --> 01:39:37,342
No anchovies.

1090
01:39:37,414 --> 01:39:39,041
Me neither.

1091
01:39:42,853 --> 01:39:45,447
Don't forget
to ditch the car soon.

1092
01:39:51,262 --> 01:39:53,230
You saved my life.

